h24 y5 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Verses 19, 20. </div><div class="t m25e x18 h24 yb99 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">16. </div><div class="t m2d8 x60 h24 y17cd ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Why was it thought unnecessary to give all the </div><div class="t m15c x27 h24 y379 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">details? Verse 21. </div><div class="t mf2f x2d h3b ya82 ff6 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lessons for Us </div><div class="t m135d x4a h24 y1652 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t mcf5 x29 h24 y1971 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The question at Jerusalem involved the whole ques-</div><div class="t m3c1 x11 h24 y16e4 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tion of salvation,— whether we have something to do </div><div class="t m1cb x11 h24 yb38 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to win salvation, or whether it is a free gift. </div><div class="t mc8 x4a h24 y1b21 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m1f8 x29 h24 y339 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">We should lay perplexing questions involving prin-</div><div class="t m3e0 x11 h24 y1bef ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ciple before the brethren for counsel. Verse 2. </div><div class="t mcb x4a h24 y605 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m87b x36 h24 y605 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Delegates were chosen to represent the various, </div><div class="t m765 x11 h24 y1f30 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">churches, and the decisions arrived at were to be re-</div><div class="t m889 x11 h24 y65 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">spected by all. Note 9. </div><div class="t mce x14 h24 y17a0 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m294 x36 h24 yf5f ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">We should report what the Lord is doing in different </div><div class="t m307 x11 h24 y194b ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fields, and how churches are being established through </div><div class="t m66e x11 h24 y1678 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the gospel message. Verse 3. </div><div class="t md1 x14 h24 y175b ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m1578 x28 h24 y188b ff4 fs16 fc0 sc